This is interesting! Looks like it is targeting the countries (AMC92) that receive #Pfizer #COVID19 #vaccine through #COVAX. 
It is dropping a #Stealer that looks for the following extensions: doc, pdf, ppt, dot, xl, csv, rtf, dot, mdb, accdb, pot, pps, ppa, rar, zip, tar, 7z https://t.co/3evpWVaYwe
